job.title: Goa Police Various Vacancy Recruitment 2021 – Apply for 1097 Vacancy
job.body:
Total Vacancies:1097

Name of the post:

  • Sub Inspector, Constable, Searcher, Asst Sub Inspector, Photographer, Laboratory Technician, Stenographer, LDC

Description:

The Goa Police Department issued a total of 1097 vacancies for the posts of Sub Inspector, Constable, Searcher, Asst Sub Inspector, Photographer, Laboratory Technician, Stenographer, LDC. The online application for these posts under Goa Police shall start soon. The eligible and interested candidates can apply for this online application before 26-05-2021. For further detailed information regarding educational qualifications, age limit, selection procedure, how to apply, etc. for these posts is mentioned below. For more such updates do visit theprograd.com .The ProGrad jobs.

 

Mode of application & application fee:

  • Mode of application: Online
  • The application fee for the General Category is INR 200/-
  • The application fee for SC/ ST/ OBC/ PWD/ EWS/ EX – Serviceman is INR 200
  • For more details, you can refer to the notification. The link is given at the bottom.

Important dates:

  • The Last date to apply online is 26-05-2021

Age limit criteria:

  • The minimum age required to apply is 18 Years
  • The maximum age required to apply is 28 Years
  • For age relaxation criteria, you can refer to the notification. The link is given below in The ProGrad jobs.

Pay Scale:

  • The pay scale as per 7th pay commission for the post of Sub Inspector, Constable, Searcher, Asst Sub Inspector, Photographer, Laboratory Technician, Stenographer, LDC is as per Government norms
  • Check the detailed notification also something has missed.

Detailed vacancies:

The vacancies in detail are given below. Check below that Goa Police issued this notification for which posts.

 

Physical eligibility:

Police Sub Inspector (Male):

  • Minimum Height – 168 cms
  • Chest (Unexpanded) – 80 cms & expanded – 85 cms
  • Running – 100 Metres in 15 Seconds
  • Lang Jump – 3.80 Metres (3 Chances)
  •  High Jump – 1.20 Metres (3 Chances)
  • 800 Metres Run in 2 Minutes 50 Seconds.

Police Sub Inspector (Female):

  • Minimum Height – 157 cms
  • Weight not Less Than 42 kgs
  • Running – 100 Metres in 19 Seconds
  • Lang Jump – 3.1 Metres (3 Chances)
  • High Jump – 0.9 Metres (3 Chances)
  • 400 Metres Run in 1 Minute 50 Seconds.

Police Constable (Male):

  • Minimum Height – 167 cms
  • Chest (Unexpanded) – 80 cms & expanded – 85 cms
  • Running – 100 Metres in 15 Seconds
  • Lang Jump – 4.00 Metres (3 Chances)
  • High Jump – 1.20 Metres (3 Chances)
  • 800 Metres Run in 3 Minutes.

Police Constable (Female):

  • Minimum Height – 157 cms
  • Weight not Less Than 42 kgs
  • Running – 100 Metres in 19 Seconds
  • Lang Jump – 3.10 Metres (3 Chances)
  • High Jump – 0.9 Metres (3 Chances)
  • 400 Metres Run in 1 Minute 50 Seconds.


How to apply for Goa Police Various Vacancy Recruitment 2021?

  • First, visit the official website.
  • Register yourself on the portal of Goa Police.
  • Login yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification of Sub Inspector, Constable, Searcher, Asst Sub Inspector, Photographer, Laboratory Technician, Stenographer, LDC.
  • Fill up the complete details that are asked in the application form.
  • Upload your photo and signature with the dimensions asked in the instructions.
  • Submit the application fee
  • Finally, download the application form for future needs.
